        "message": "=<div style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;max-width:580px;margin:0 auto;color:#111;line-height:1.6;\">\n<p>Hi {{ $('Parse AI + Generate Slots + ID').first().json.firstName }},</p>\n<p>Thanks for reaching out about <strong>{{ $('Parse AI + Generate Slots + ID').first().json.service }}</strong>. I'd love to connect over a free 30-minute strategy call.</p>\n<p>Here are my available slots — all times are in <strong>IST (Bangalore, India, UTC+5:30)</strong>:</p>\n<div style=\"background:#f5f5ff;border-left:4px solid #6366f1;padding:16px;border-radius:6px;margin:20px 0;\">\n{{ $('Parse AI + Generate Slots + ID').first().json.slotsHTML }}\n</div>\n<p><strong>Reply to this email</strong> with the option number that works for you — e.g. <em>\"Option 2 works for me\"</em> — and I'll confirm your booking with a Google Meet link right away.</p>\n<p>If none of these times work, just tell me your preferred window.</p>\n<p>Best,<br><strong>Omkar Biradar</strong><br>AI Automation Consultant<br>omkar13884@gmail.com | +91 99727 34513</p>\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:1px solid #eee;margin:24px 0;\">\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;color:#aaa;\">Ref: {{ $('Parse AI + Generate Slots + ID').first().json.submissionId }} — keep this in your reply so I can match your booking.</p>\n</div>",
